[Maps of Bulgaria can be seen at http://tinyurl.com/zl6ygn8 and https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4167379,52870. Radievo is a village in the municipality of Dimitrovgrad, in Haskovo Province.

Similar information from Radievo, accompanied by photographs showing the veterinary team engaged in the disease-control activities and of demonstrating farmers, is available at http://tinyurl.com/h7gf65r (in Bulgarian).

As commented earlier, the odds of success in controlling the further spread of lumpy skin disease within a country bordering an lumpy skin disease-endemic area by stamping out without vaccination are rather meagre. - Mod.AS]
